text: Istiqlol futbol klubi is an Uzbekistani football club based in Fergana. The club plays in Uzbekistan Pro League. ==History== The club was formed 2016 under the name Istiqlol in Fergana. ==References== Category:Football clubs in Uzbekistan Category:Association football clubs established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in Uzbekistan
title: FC Istiqlol Fergana
